queryResponse.sql:
SELECT * FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z___pivot_row_rank, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY z__pivot_col_rank ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z__pivot_col_ordering, CASE WHEN z___min_rank = z___rank THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS z__is_highest_ranked_cell FROM (
SELECT *, MIN(z___rank) OVER (PARTITION BY "shipments.lane_city_state") as z___min_rank FROM (
SELECT *, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN z__pivot_col_rank=1 THEN (CASE WHEN "shipments.total_margin_average" IS NOT NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) ELSE 2 END, CASE WHEN z__pivot_col_rank=1 THEN "shipments.total_margin_average" ELSE NULL END DESC, "shipments.total_margin_average" DESC, z__pivot_col_rank, "shipments.lane_city_state") AS z___rank FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN "first_pickup_region.name" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "first_pickup_region.name" DESC, CASE WHEN "shipments.is_drop_trailer" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "shipments.is_drop_trailer") AS z__pivot_col_rank FROM (
SELECT
    first_pickup_region.name  AS "first_pickup_region.name",
        (CASE WHEN coalesce(first_pickup.is_drop_trailer or last_delivery.is_drop_trailer, false)  THEN 'Yes' ELSE 'No' END) AS "shipments.is_drop_trailer",
    ((initcap(trim(first_pickup.city, ', '))) || ', ' || (upper(trim(first_pickup.state_code)))) || ' > ' || ((initcap(trim(last_delivery.city, ', '))) || ', ' || (upper(trim(last_delivery.state_code))))  AS "shipments.lane_city_state",
    AVG(( shipments.shipper_total_rate-(iff(shipments.carrier_application_id is null, null, shipments.carrier_total_rate))  ) ) AS "shipments.total_margin_average"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipment_stops  AS first_pickup ON first_pickup.shipment_id=shipments.id and first_pickup.first_stop and (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(first_pickup.deprecated_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')) is null
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.lk_regions  AS first_pickup_region ON (upper(trim(first_pickup.state_code)))=first_pickup_region.state_code
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipment_stops  AS last_delivery ON last_delivery.shipment_id=shipments.id and last_delivery.last_stop and (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(last_delivery.deprecated_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')) is null
WHERE ((( shipments.dispatched_at  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( shipments.dispatched_at  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', 6, DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AND (first_pickup_region.name ) <> 'Canada'
GROUP BY
    1,
    2,
    3) ww
) bb WHERE z__pivot_col_rank <= 16384
) aa
) xx
) zz
 WHERE (z__pivot_col_rank <= 50 OR z__is_highest_ranked_cell = 1) AND (z___pivot_row_rank <= 500 OR z__pivot_col_ordering = 1) ORDER BY z___pivot_row_rank
